{"tid":1120706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大校長史維：與廣州分校「教學行政資源互通」　師生發展機會更大","createTime":"2019-04-23T00:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T04:30:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3e5b9e525dc5a84c6e152d34181b1c48e9c1cb23","tid":1120706,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:05:33.000Z","msg":"科大校長史維：與廣州分校「教學行政資源互通」　師生發展機會更大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/274346/%e7%a7%91%e5%a4%a7%e6%a0%a1%e9%95%b7%e5%8f%b2%e7%b6%ad%ef%bc%9a%e8%88%87%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e5%88%86%e6%a0%a1%e3%80%8c%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8%e8%a1%8c%e6%94%bf%e8%b3%87%e6%ba%90%e4%ba%92%e9%80%9a%e3%80%8d/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F274346%2F%25e7%25a7%2591%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e9%2595%25b7%25e5%258f%25b2%25e7%25b6%25ad%25ef%25bc%259a%25e8%2588%2587%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e5%2588%2586%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%2595%2599%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%2594%25bf%25e8%25b3%2587%25e6%25ba%2590%25e4%25ba%2592%25e9%2580%259a%25e3%2580%258d%2F&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=eb30a7b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/274346/%e7%a7%91%e5%a4%a7%e6%a0%a1%e9%95%b7%e5%8f%b2%e7%b6%ad%ef%bc%9a%e8%88%87%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e5%88%86%e6%a0%a1%e3%80%8c%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8%e8%a1%8c%e6%94%bf%e8%b3%87%e6%ba%90%e4%ba%92%e9%80%9a%e3%80%8d/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港科技大學正籌備在廣州設立分校，校長史維接受商台訪問時表示，分校預計在3年後落成，香港本部與廣州分校會在保證財政資源獨立的情況下，採用教學及行政資源互通方式運作。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">史維舉例稱，同一教授可在本部與分校獲「交叉任命」、實驗室等設施可開放予兩校師生使用、兩校學生可互相選讀課程，畢業時獲兩校頒發雙學位證書。他相信這模式會令師生得到更大發展機會。他又指，兩校人員往來頻繁，香港學生應尊重大陸制度，雖校方願意盡力支援大學師生，但要求凌駕大陸制度是不切實際。<br />\n</span><br />\n雖然史維多次受訪都強調本部資源不會被「分薄」，然而《蘋果日報》上月引述科大消息人士指，循該校去年推出的自願離職方案離職之員工，將重新獲廣州分校前期辦公室聘用，疑為分校預留資源而削減本部開支。"},{"pid":"3f7cc755b544a0caebaa483a8616091a4862ce3c","tid":1120706,"uid":50457,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:10:03.000Z","msg":"(廣州)師生發展更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好明顯寫少兩個字"},{"pid":"2212c21528457fd6ee8881b11d11cfd6b81e1860","tid":1120706,"uid":249885,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:20:02.000Z","msg":"屎為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f502abc4e568e0124a257c622cf9775527ede7","tid":1120706,"uid":47674,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:23:25.000Z","msg":"台灣啲老嘢總係對大陸有幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be81d6a5f33f064e9da2b044bc6d46dc041464f","tid":1120706,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:26:50.000Z","msg":"又係台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45286ba054fd82760a65b18e8e16634d8d4bacf","tid":1120706,"uid":316,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:37:10.000Z","msg":"又可以借香港個名去偷人研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed9a8bc9a641392b8eaa324363f75165dd75d2c","tid":1120706,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5dd65efb1b5f3ddbfb4097bd9a689437c580b8","tid":1120706,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"科大雖然紅底，但一直以黎知道咩叫明哲保身<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441b55ad66daa0806026d914dcfa898488045dab","tid":1120706,"uid":18774,"like":0,"d